Wednesday, December 14, 1994

MERIT DOCKET

94-2153. State ex rel. Scripps Howard Broadcasting Co. v. Cuyahoga Cty. Court of Common Pleas, Juv. Div. In Prohibition.

On motion to consolidate with 94-2155, infra. Motion granted. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
